"Playing in Costa Rica is a dream come true"
In the exclusive interview with Viva, bassist Jeff Ament of Pearl Jam says the band is ready to give one of their best concerts at the National Stadium next Sunday.
For more than 20 years they were expected, but the band ensures that a dream comes true for them when they play in Costa Rica.
This was assured by the group’s bassist and co-founder, Jeff Ament, who gave Viva last week from Brazil an exclusive interview.
